<!--
	
(Now hosted on Github)

Tag names are case and name sensitive. For best results, always use absolute paths.

<slide>
	<file> - required
	location of media to be loaded
		jpg, jpeg, gif, swf, png for images
		flv, mov, mp4, m4v for videos (file has to be flv or encoded with h.264 in container formats)
		mp3 for audio
	
	<thumb> - optional
	should be sized within the constraint of the thumbWidth/thumbHeight, but will be scaled as necessary to fit
	
	<still> - optional
	location of freeze frame when playing a video, should be a jpg still at the native size of the video
	
-->


